ITIL Change management
In ITIL Change management the focus should not only be on hardware and software, other services should be taken into consideration to establish a fully functional IT system. The entire management system should be prioritized in order to properly execute each one accordingly. 
When implementing changes, carefully take into consideration the standard, Normal, and Emergency changes so that the different stages can be properly prioritized. 
